( @adamriver8 ) Image 54 of 54 San Antonio has wild Thursday night with Luke Bryan, Young Thug shows 1 / 54 Back to Gallery Bro-country singer Luke Bryan and rapper Young Thug are anything but similar, but the two put on some rowdy concerts in San Antonio Thursday night to start the weekend off early.
While Bryan played at the Alamodome downtown, Young Thug was at the much smaller, but still popular, millennial-crazed Club Rio in the North Side.
RELATED: REVIEW: Lionel Richie 'All Night Long' – almost
Instagram photos of the gigs show that thousands of people had a wild Thursday, no matter if they spent the night in cowboy boots or skin-tight dresses and stilettos.
While Bryan fans posted #CountryConcertsAreTheBest and #INeedACowboyHat, Young Thug admirers posted they were “thug ready” and “stupid turnt.”
Yes, it sounds like a wild night, indeed.
Click through the slideshow to see photos of San Antonio’s rowdy Thursday night.
